features.text:
Welcome to "On the Blockchain" - A digital community art wall. Join us from Sept 9th - 3pm-5pm in the metaverse or in person at the Vermillion Art Gallery + Bar in Capitol Hill, Seattle. Stop by and we can assist you in pinning up your art and NFTs. You can always come back by visiting: http://OnTheBlockChain.land in any web browser.

Presented by On The Block and BlockChain Events.

Last updated 9/21/23
